            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-37e4779a-63ec-49cc-8261-bfeaf2f04fb7">
                The Minister of Food (Mr. Strachey)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-37e4779a-63ec-49cc-8261-bfeaf2f04fb7" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
