        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-73595009-425c-4088-8382-81a467cd69ce">
                Mr. Hogg
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-73595009-425c-4088-8382-81a467cd69ce" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1946-07-18/debates/8ed097fb-a5fa-4459-9c7a-4b355d9cf9de/Bread(Rationing)Order#contribution-73595009-425c-4088-8382-81a467cd69ce">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Surely, it depends upon the size of the ration. What I was endeavouring to argue was that a system which depended upon keeping children and housewives short was a bad system.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-73595009-425c-4088-8382-81a467cd69ce" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1946-07-18/debates/8ed097fb-a5fa-4459-9c7a-4b355d9cf9de/Bread(Rationing)Order#contribution-73595009-425c-4088-8382-81a467cd69ce">
