<p class="">The hon. Member has intervened at the precise moment at which I was about to say—and I ask the House to believe this—that I do not <span id="1526" class="column-number" data-column-number="1526"></span> associate myself with any reproaches against the Government for having acquiesced in any excessive allocation of wheat to the distressed areas of Europe.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
